# hoteldistro.com — Cursor Rules

## Stack
- Next.js 15 (App Router)
- TypeScript (strict)
- Tailwind CSS v4
- MDX via next-mdx-remote/rsc
- Deployed on Vercel

## Architecture
- Chapters live in `src/content/chapters/` as `.mdx` files with frontmatter
- Dynamic routing at `/chapters/[slug]`
- Password auth via middleware + cookie (`hdistro_auth`)
- Exhibits (images) in `public/exhibits/`

## Conventions
- Use `@/` import alias for `src/`
- Server Components by default; `"use client"` only when needed
- No inline styles — Tailwind only
- Inter font via next/font/google
- Clean, minimal UI — lots of whitespace, sharp typography
- Prose styling via `@tailwindcss/typography`

## File Naming
- Components: PascalCase (`ChapterNav.tsx`)
- Utils/lib: camelCase (`chapters.ts`)
- MDX content: kebab-case (`distribution-101.mdx`)

## Security
- All routes gated by middleware except `/login` and `/api/auth`
- Never expose `SITE_PASSWORD` client-side
